                <expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">S</supplied>ex</abbr><ex>to</ex></expan> Pedio <expan><abbr>Sex</abbr><ex>ti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> Ar<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ensi</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="2"/>Lusiano Hirruto <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>prim</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pil</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XXI pra<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>ef</abbr><ex>ecto</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="4"/>Raetis Vindolicis valli<supplied reason="lost">s</supplied> <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">P</supplied>oeninae et levis <expan><abbr>armatur</abbr><ex>ae</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>IIIIvir</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>ure</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>icundo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ecto</ex></expan> Germanic<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied> <lb n="7"/>Caesaris quinquennalici <lb n="8"/>iuris ex <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>enatus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>onsulto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>quinquen</abbr><ex>nali</ex></expan> iterum <lb n="9"/>hic amphitheatrum <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ua</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ecunia</ex></expan> fecit <lb n="10"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Dullius <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> Gallus
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Geringfügige Abweichungen. - (C): Bautätigkeit für die Stadt Interpromium. Das erwähnte Amphitheater ist jedoch jenes von Teate Marrucinorum, der Stadt, in welcher Sex. Pedius Lusianus Hirrutus das Amt eines IIIIvir iure dicundo innehatte. - Tribus Arn(ensis) statt An(iensis) ist nun durch Buonocore gesichert.</p>
            </div>
